text: Eadweard, & Eadmund, & Æðelred Æðelingas syndon Eadgares suna Cyninges.
Ingeld wæs Ines broðor west Seaxna Cyninges, & he heold rice vii & xxx wintra.
And he getimbrade þæt beorhte mynster æt Glæstingbyrig, & æfter þam fyrde to Sancte Petres & þær his feorh asealde.
And hi begen broðra wæron Cenredes suna.
Se Scef wæs Noes sunu, & he wæs innan þære earce geboren.
Et Adam primus homo. Et pater omnium qui eft Christus.
